
Accounts required: io.adafruit.com;  ifttt;

platform: espeasy; sonoff or esp hw; ifttt; io.adafruit.com (mqttt)
----------------

1. flash sonoff with espeasy mega

2. sonoff hw: 

relay gpio12 

led gpio13

sw gpio0


espeasy setup setup:
controllers:
io.adafruit.com
user: kenkoknz1
pw: aoi

subscribe feed: kenkoknz1/feeds/# 

publish feed: e.g kenkoknz1/feeds/%tskname%%valname%        create a feed temp1temp

ie kenkok/feeds/temp1/temp



----
pulish template:
kenkoknz1/feeds/%tskname%%valname%        create a feed temp1temp

ie kenkok/feeds/temp1/temp



subscribe:
kenkoknz1/feeds/#                       e.g create a feed cmd;   send mqtt: kenkoknz1/feeds/cmd with payload gpio,12,1


------------------------------









